	<string>Hidden Hiqmah uses your location to show accurate prayer times and the Qiblah direction for where you are. You can also enter a city manually instead.</string>
	<key>NSLocationAlwaysAndWhenInUseUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Hidden Hiqmah uses your location to show accurate prayer times and the Qiblah direction for where you are. You can also enter a city manually instead.</string>
	<key>NSMicrophoneUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Hidden Hiqmah uses the microphone so you can record your Qur'an recitation and play it back while memorizing.</string>
	<key>NSMotionUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Hidden Hiqmah uses the compass to point you toward the Qiblah.</string>
